From <a href="http://nesdevwiki.org/wiki/index.php/NTSC_Video" class="postlink">the wiki page</a>:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">25  sync<br />4   black<br />15  colorburst<br />5   black<br />1   pulse<br />15  left border &#40;background color&#41;<br />256 active<br />11  right border &#40;background color&#41;<br />9   black</div><br />Sync is below black level, so would appear as black. Colorburst is like color $18 (maybe $28, but definitely that hue). Pulse is a mid-gray.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=17">blargg</a> — Wed Aug 22, 2007 12:41 pm</p><hr />
